d services, including devops automation, cloud and hosting, managed cloud, monitoring, network security, server management, and helpdesk services; and integro corporate lending solutions, comprising loan origination system, financial analysis, limits management system, collateral management system, trade limit, early warning system, and document management system; and phygital customer experience. Further, it offers G to G Solutions, E-governance public, and smart city services. Aurionpro Solutions Limited was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Navi Mumbai, India."}}